messages.text: I’m going to wear red! Let’s match.
Don’t tell me you forgot again!?
I’m sorry babe. I totally forgot.
You always do this to me.
This is the third time you forgot about our date.
I just got so busy with med finals.
I didn’t mean to forget about our date.
Rach, you know I love you.
I’ll make it up to you I promise.
Because I got a surprise for you!
Can you at least give me a hint?
I don’t want to guess anymore…
I don’t want a weapon as a gift.
Come on Babe! You are so close to figuring it out.
Okay, I’ll give you another clue.
You hid a weapon in my room!!!
What if my mom sees it?
It’s not that big a deal.
I thought the gift was a surprise?!
Where did you hide the weapon!?
I don’t want you ruin the surprise.
Bert! Tell me where it is right now.
I love you so much Rachel.
HOW DO I STOP THE TIMER!?
